<lyrics>[V1]
 1- knt wḥdy tạyh fy ẓlạmy ʿạysẖ w ʿnạdy w ậtẖạmy jrãḥwny yạ yswʿ
 qrạr- ạ̹nt ạldwạ ljrwḥy ạ̹nt ạlly tḥyy rwḥy
 ạ̹nt ạlly tsẖbʿ jwʿy rạjʿ w kly ḥnyn
 rạjʿ w rạfʿ ạ̹ydy rạjʿ ạ̹lyk yạ sydy
 rạjʿ w sẖwqy ạ̹lyk msẖtạq ạ̉kwn llfạdy kl ʿmry
 2- ạ̉sẖky lmyn hmy ạ̹nt ạldfạ w ạ̹nt ạlạ̉mạn
 myn ybʿdk ʿny
 lmạ bkwn tʿbạn msẖ ḥạss bạlạ̉mạn
 tmd ạ̹ydyk yạ yswʿ tsẖfyny bạlạ̹ymạn</lyrics>
<title>knt wḥdy</title>
</song>